 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>20 things we learned in 2010</h1>
		
					<p itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                        	        data-component="Article:standfirst_cta"			>It was a year in which game-changing developments in social media competed with a new political turf wars over the 'squeezed middle'. Here a team of Observer writers and experts chart the concepts, trends and buzzwords that defined the last year and are likely to shape the next one</p>
		
		
  	</div>

